      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "to read a kanji with a different pronunciation",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "この漢字は文脈によって「ふく」とも「いる」とも読み替えることができる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "昔の文献を読むときは、現代の感覚で言葉を読み替えないように注意が必要だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "先生が難しい古文の表現を、分かりやすい現代語に読み替えて説明してくれた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "to load (e.g. data on a computer)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
